desc: One stop dog boutique that offers the latest in fashion trends for your spoiled pooch. Shop from our best selection of everyday dog dresses & shirts, luxury dog dresses, dog umbrellas, dog sunglasses, dog raincoats, choke free harnesses and more.

layout.text: Be The Envy Of The Park

At One Spoiled Pooch (OSP), we believe that your dog is an extended member of your family and should be treated as so. If you are wearing the best, your best friend should be too! We offer the best brands in dog apparel and accessories to make your dog, One Spoiled Pooch.
